StatefulSet
===========
Two type of workloads

1.Pods
2.Controllers

Controllers
===========
1.Deployment
2.Statefulset
3.Daemonset
4.Jobs

A controller which is managing the pod.

Specialities
=============
1.Unique network identifiers
2.stable persistant storage
3.Ordered graceful deployment and scaling
4.Ordered automated rolling updates.

Each pod is accessing a different volume.

When the application dies it can resume from the same state from where it left.


How to shutdown the statefulset?
Write in one pod 
and read from another pod.


1.Storage class is across namespace.
2.namespace are virtual cluster on top of physical clusters.

Suppose we need to change enviroment variables on fly we can do these 
